{% comment %}
  Free Gift Engine — app EMBED. This is the ENGINE: it loads the storefront controller site-wide
  (every page, so it reacts to the cart drawer opening from anywhere) and renders a hidden config
  element the controller reads.

  Enable it in the theme editor under: Theme settings (gear) -> App embeds -> "Free Gift Engine".

  Phase 5b-2b-1: the perception UI is INJECTED into the cart-drawer flow (blended, not a floating
  overlay) — a slim progress stepper under the "Your cart" header and the "Choose your free gift"
  chooser below the line items. Both are re-injected on every drawer re-render. The free gift renders
  normally in the cart list at $0 (we don't hide it). Choices come from the shopper's selection (the
  `default_choices` seam was retired in 5b-2a).

  PORTABILITY: the controller auto-detects the cart drawer + its anchors (Dawn's <cart-drawer>,
  `.drawer__header`, `#CartDrawer-CartItems`, `.drawer__footer`), with a safe fallback if anchors
  aren't found. If a production theme differs, override the drawer element without code:
    data-drawer-selector="<css selector for the drawer element>"
{% endcomment %}

<div
  data-fge-app-block
  data-proxy-path="/apps/free-gift/validate"
  data-presentment-currency="{{ cart.currency.iso_code }}"
  data-country="{{ localization.country.iso_code }}"
  hidden
></div>

<script src="{{ 'free-gift.js' | asset_url }}" defer></script>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Free Gift Engine",
  "target": "body",
  "settings": []
}
{% endschema %}
